Available Tools: create_folder | move_file | copy_file | rename_file | delete_file | list_folder
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "path": "string", "destination": "string", "new_name": "string" }
Response Schema: { "path": "string", "entries": [{ "name": "string", "type": "file|folder", "size_bytes": number }], "status": "string" }
---
Question: Generate a directory labeled "Sales_Data_2025" under the reports hierarchy.
Call: { "func_call": "create_folder", "path": "/reports/Sales_Data_2025", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/reports", "entries": [{ "name": "Sales_Data_2025", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "summary.csv", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 51200 }], "status": "success" }

Question: Relocate "quarterly_targets.xlsx" from the temp uploads area to the reports/Sales_Data_2025 container.
Call: { "func_call": "move_file", "path": "/temp/uploads/quarterly_targets.xlsx", "destination": "/reports/Sales_Data_2025", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/reports/Sales_Data_2025", "entries": [{ "name": "quarterly_targets.xlsx", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 89000 }], "status": "success" }

